content: App used to be good but the interface is lacking and all of the recipes that used to be there are now gone. The interface isn't intuitive and causes recipes to get "reported" deleting them from view. Sucks I used to love this app. Do not buy it.
There's not even alot of vegan recipes on there at all and there's little to no effort done on the UI of the app itself especially for something that you PAID for

I love that this app gives me so many ideas for recipes. I can also add to the community. I like how it's people contributing to the app because that is what we need when starting out as vegans, meal ideas. People help out people, it's a great app.
worked at first now its blank what's the point and I paid for it 😤 not working again 😒😒 Still not working session token expired keep coming up no response from developers joke 😒😒

Excellent, informative, app that's has evolved significantly for the better. This app has my full support.

Was very excited to see this application & referred a number of people to it. I PAID to support these efforts even with questionable post on social media. When I commented about ONE concern on sharing potentially fake info, not only did I start getting messages from someone associated with this company, they also started posting on my personal page & I was also blocked from the page. Very disappointed.
